            {
              "message": "`cargo make track-pr-merge` is documented as a live merge-path command, but this wrapper no longer exists in `Makefile.toml`; the current CLI exposes the merge path as `bin/sotp pr wait-and-merge` and `/track:merge` still has command docs. Leaving the removed wrapper in the new convention reintroduces a dead command reference for readers following the branch policy.",
