              "line": 25,
              "category": "consistency"
            },
            {
              "message": "The updated priority reference says `.claude/rules/` is limited to 08/09/10/07, but `.claude/rules/01-language.md` still exists and is part of the planned final operating-rule set. Agents following this narrowed comment can skip the language policy rules, so the reference should include 01 or avoid enumerating an incomplete subset.",
