              "message": "The replacement leaves two of the three convention references as bare filenames (`track-lifecycle.md` and `git-notes.md`). This command section is a list of architecture-facing document paths to update, and those bare paths do not exist at the repo root or relative to this command file, so agents following the command can miss the required convention docs after `track/workflow.md` is deleted. Use the full `knowledge/conventions/track-lifecycle.md` and `knowledge/conventions/git-notes.md` paths here.",
