        {
          "type": "fast",
          "verdict": "findings_remain",
          "findings": [
            {
              "message": "The new prerequisites section still omits the host Rust/Cargo toolchain even though the first documented setup step is `cargo make bootstrap`, and that bootstrap task hard-fails when `cargo` is missing. As written, a fresh machine with Docker but without Rust will hit a setup failure immediately.",
